<section class="page-journal-club">

  <!-- Journal Club logo (replaces CSS orb) -->
  <div class="page-journal-club__logo-wrap">
    <img
      src="{{ 'Journal_Club_logo.webp' | asset_url }}"
      alt="Journal Club"
      class="page-journal-club__logo"
    >
  </div>

  <!-- Hero: tagline, quote, hero sign-up -->
  <div class="page-journal-club__hero">
    <p class="page-journal-club__tagline">
      Transform your weekend from mindless scrolling to mindful reflection.<br>
      25 minutes of guided meditation, journaling, and authentic connection.
    </p>

    <p class="page-journal-club__hero-quote">
      &#8220;Every week I cannot wait for our time together. That dedicated time where we untangle the week, observe our patterns and practice acceptance.&#8221;
    </p>

    <!-- Hero sign-up: styled like Seeker Drop + Add to Cart -->
    <div class="page-journal-club__hero-signup">
      <script async data-uid="a433277e18" src="https://hyper-real-love-2.kit.com/a433277e18/index.js"></script>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Member count + badges -->
  <div class="page-journal-club__meta">
    <p class="page-journal-club__member-count">
      <span class="page-journal-club__dot"></span>
      126 seekers
    </p>
    <div class="page-journal-club__badges">
      <span>🌍 it's online</span>
      <span>✍️ it's free</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Long-form body -->
  <div class="page-journal-club__body">
    <p>An easy regular ritual to take time to untangle and work on your Self. We meet Saturday mornings. 25 minutes. Meditation, journaling, connection. Free.</p>

    <p><strong>Join the club and start your weekend with intention.</strong></p>

    <blockquote class="page-journal-club__body-quote">
      &#8220;Every week I cannot wait for our time together. Even when I&#8217;m rushing through the chaos of daily life, I think about Saturday morning &#8212; that dedicated time where we untangle the week, observe our patterns and practice acceptance.&#8221;
    </blockquote>

    <p>This is your invitation to wake up. To practice the art of being present in a world that demands you be everywhere else.</p>

    <p><strong>Join us every Saturday morning (CEST) online.</strong> Something we can do together, even when we&#8217;re not in the same city.</p>

    <p class="page-journal-club__minutes-title"><strong>What happens in our 25 minutes:</strong></p>
    <ul class="page-journal-club__minutes-list">
      <li>5 minutes: Guided meditation to settle in</li>
      <li>15 minutes: Private journaling with weekly reflection questions</li>
      <li>5 minutes: Gentle close</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>How to join:</strong> From anywhere with just pen, paper, and your phone or laptop. Google Meet link shared in our WhatsApp group. Your writing stays completely yours — we journal together but individually.</p>

    <p>Never journaled before? Think of it as writing a letter to yourself. No sharing required, no perfect pages needed.</p>


    <!-- Bottom sign-up: "Join the Club" -->
    <p class="page-journal-club__bottom-label">Before we journal together, let&#8217;s start here:</p>

    <div class="page-journal-club__bottom-signup">
      <script async data-uid="a433277e18" src="https://hyper-real-love-2.kit.com/a433277e18/index.js"></script>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

